high_descs: Turn right, face counter with coffee maker on it.
Turn left, proceed until microwave on right.  Turn right to face microwave.
Open microwave door, put mug in and close door.  Wait three seconds, open door, remove mug and close door.
Turn around, cross room to counter.
Open cabinet to right below counter, put mug in directly behind bottle, close cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Move mug from coffee maker to microwave and heat, move to cabinet.

high_descs: turn to the right twice and take a few steps and turn to the left facing the counter top
take the cup from the coffee maker on the counter top
turn to the left and go the the front of the microwave and turn to the right facing the microwave
put the cup in the microwave and heat it and when finish heating take out the cup from the microwave
turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the right and go to the counter
open the bottom right counter door and put the cup in it and close the door
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup in the bottom of the counter

high_descs: turn around and walk over to the coffee maker on the kitchen counter to the left
grab the coffee mug out from underneath the coffee maker spout
turn left and walk over to the microwave at the end of the room on the right
place the cup inside the microwave, let the microwave microwave the cup for a bit, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the kitchen counter to the right of the sink at the end of the room
place the cup inside of the cabinet to the bottom right of the sink under the kitchen counter
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved coffee mug inside of the kitchen cabinet
